16:02.892 --> 16:05.816
And I said, do you have the tidescript to Greenville's Act?

16:05.836 --> 16:06.237
He said, yes.

16:06.998 --> 16:09.762
I've given that to my daughter.

16:09.782 --> 16:18.213
And so then the daughter had all this material.

16:18.674 --> 16:19.515
And I phoned her.

16:19.555 --> 16:24.642
And she said, why don't you come over, I haven't gone through it yet.

16:24.662 --> 16:26.024
Why don't you come down and we'll go through it.

16:26.384 --> 16:27.846
And I really didn't want to have that much

16:28.231 --> 16:31.736
financial and emotional investment, unless I was going to be able to buy it.

16:31.756 --> 16:39.708
So I said, you go through it, list what's there, and send me the list, and I'll make you an offer, or we'll talk about it after you know what it is.

16:39.748 --> 16:43.694
So it took her about two or three months to do that, and a couple other phone calls.

